Now, to get our
program started, please

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:17.600
join me in welcoming Yukio
Lippit to the podium.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:20.030
Yukio is a professor
of art and architecture

00:05:20.030 --> 00:05:22.880
at Harvard, an expert
in Japanese art

00:05:22.880 --> 00:05:24.860
