00:05:48.206 --> 00:05:49.580
In the greater
Boston area, we're

00:05:49.580 --> 00:05:52.760
fortunate enough to have art
museums of the highest caliber.

00:05:52.760 --> 00:05:55.700
The Museum of Fine Arts is
one of the great encyclopedic

00:05:55.700 --> 00:05:58.040
museums anywhere in the
world, with collections second

00:05:58.040 --> 00:05:59.270
to none.

00:05:59.270 --> 00:06:01.490
The Isabella Stewart
Gardner Museum close by

00:06:01.490 --> 00:06:03.950
is a real cultural treasure
of the city of Boston,

00:06:03.950 --> 00:06:06.650
one of the remarkable
museums that emerged out

00:06:06.650 --> 00:06:09.290
of the Gilded Age, and
its collections housed

00:06:09.290 --> 00:06:11.690
in an unforgettable setting.

00:06:11.690 --> 00:06:14.210
Through dynamic programming
and landmark exhibitions,

00:06:14.210 --> 00:06:16.460
the Institute of
Contemporary Ar in Boston

00:06:16.460 --> 00:06:18.980
has been a leader
in the art world

00:06:18.980 --> 00:06:21.290
since its opening in the 1930s.

00:06:21.290 --> 00:06:23.900
Similarly, the List Center
for the Visual Arts at MIT

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:27.380
