joined by our longer-serving

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:30.770
directors, Jill
Medvedow and Paul Ha,

00:08:30.770 --> 00:08:33.750
in a wide-ranging discussion
here at the Radcliffe Institute

00:08:33.750 --> 00:08:37.159
for our Harvard
Radcliffe community,

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:40.070
about the museum, the
city, and the university.

00:08:40.070 --> 00:08:42.152
And somehow, we succeeded.

00:08:42.152 --> 00:08:43.610
It goes without
saying that they're

00:08:43.610 --> 00:08:45.193
extraordinarily busy
people, and we're

00:08:45.193 --> 00:08:47.600
extremely grateful for
their time and enthusiasm

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:49.020
in joining us today.

