And before introducing
our participants

00:08:50.660 --> 00:08:52.450
and inviting them
to the stage, let

00:08:52.450 --> 00:08:55.580
me just say a few words about
how this evening will proceed.

00:08:55.580 --> 00:08:58.850
After our roughly
hour-long discussion,

00:08:58.850 --> 00:09:01.340
