00:09:42.110 --> 00:09:46.280
at the Morgan Library and Museum
before moving here in 2016

00:09:46.280 --> 00:09:48.500
to become the Norma
Jean Calderwood

00:09:48.500 --> 00:09:51.020
Director of the Gardner Museum.

