know here, she oversaw

00:10:43.010 --> 00:10:46.670
the building and opening in
2006 of the current ICA building

00:10:46.670 --> 00:10:48.380
in the Seaport District
in South Boston,

00:10:48.380 --> 00:10:52.427
which has become a true
cultural landmark of the city.

